# MCP servers (UpNext workspace)

Use **only** the UpNext-prefixed MCP servers defined in `.cursor/mcp.json`:

- `upnext-supabase` — Supabase for the UpNext project (not Simtem2026 or invoice)
- `upnext-stripe` — Stripe for UpNext
- `upnext-vercel` — Vercel for UpNext
- `upnext-resend` — Resend for UpNext (`UPNEXT_RESEND_API_KEY` env var)

**Do not** call global MCP servers from other projects (`supabase - Simtem2026`, `supabase invoice`, `revenuecat`, `upstash`, etc.). Those stay disabled in this workspace.

When `project_ref` is known, pin Supabase with:
`https://mcp.supabase.com/mcp?project_ref=<UPNEXT_SUPABASE_PROJECT_REF>`

First use of OAuth MCPs (Supabase, Stripe, Vercel) requires signing in to the **UpNext** accounts in Cursor Settings → MCP.
